'''2017年世界公路自行车锦标赛'''是第90届[[世界公路自行车锦标赛|世界公路自行车锦标赛]]，于2017年9月17日至24日在挪威卑尔根进行<ref name=Bergen>{{cite web|title=UCI Management Committee agrees key decisions|url=http://www.uci.ch/pressreleases/uci-management-committee-agrees-key-decisions/|date=2014-09-25|publisher=[[国际自行车联合会|UCI]]|accessdate=2014-09-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140927071441/http://www.uci.ch/pressreleases/uci-management-committee-agrees-key-decisions/|archivedate=2014-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是挪威第二次主办世界公路自行车锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/gbcyclingteam/article/20170913-gb-cyclingteam-Race-guide--2017-UCI-Road-World-Championships---Bergen--Norway-0|title=Race guide: 2017 UCI Road World Championships|work=British Cycling|date=2017-09-14|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915165012/https://www.britishcycling.org.uk/gbcyclingteam/article/20170913-gb-cyclingteam-Race-guide--2017-UCI-Road-World-Championships---Bergen--Norway-0|archivedate=2017-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卑尔根于2014年9月25日击败[[奥地利|奥地利]][[因斯布鲁克|因斯布鲁克]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[墨尔本|墨尔本]]和[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]][[波哥大|波哥大]]，获得该届世锦赛主办权<ref name="Norway bid">{{cite news|last=Knöfler|first=Lukas|title=Norway leads race to host 2017 Worlds|url=http://www.cyclingquotes.com/news/norway_leads_race_to_host_2017_worlds/|date=2014-02-07|publisher=cyclingquotes.com|accessdate=2014-04-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209165626/http://www.cyclingquotes.com/news/norway_leads_race_to_host_2017_worlds/|archivedate=2014-02-09}}{{cbignore}}</ref><ref name=Bergen/>。

